thread.title: DAVID
thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by DAVID

author: DAVID
title: DAVID
text: The service provided at the counter in Sydney Airport was good and prompt. We were able to get a car despite not having any booking. However, the car boot was not cleaned properly as there were leftover food rubbish from previous customer. The petrol tank was not full and we had to go back to the counter from the parking lot to inform the counter service person. As we had just came in from our long flight, it was quite tiring for us to do so.
